file.name: parameters.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
paths:
components:
    parameters:
        DateInserted:
            name: dateInserted
            in: query
            description: >
                Filter by insert date. See [date filters](https://docs.vanillaforums.com/help/apiv2/date-filters/).
            schema:
                format: date-filter
                type: string
        DateUpdated:
            name: dateUpdated
            in: query
            description: >
                Filter by update date. See [date filters](https://docs.vanillaforums.com/help/apiv2/date-filters/).
            schema:
                format: date-filter
                type: string
        Page:
            name: page
            in: query
            description: >
                Page number. See [Pagination](https://docs.vanillaforums.com/apiv2/#pagination).
            schema:
                type: integer
                default: 1
                minimum: 1
        Offset:
            name: offset
            in: query
            description: >
                Similar to a page parameter, but specifies a specific numeric record offset starting at zero.
            schema:
                type: integer
                minimum: 0
